data.description: Situated on 1/2 acre, this charming home in Rayburn Country, is perfect for someone looking for peace and privacy.Property backs up to greenbelt and 700 acres of timber land!  Located just minutes from the boat ramps on Lake Sam Rayburn and a golf cart ride away from Rayburn Resort. This 1565 square foot home has a large living room that opens up to the spacious kitchen. The back deck is wonderful for entertaining! Granite countertops throughout, stained concrete flooring, high ceilings, oversized garage for boat parking, and so much more! Home comes fully furnished except for a few personal items! This is a must see!
